    <text>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_2d37ca29">
            <lb />The Welte Mignon</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_49bbbbff">
            <lb />
            <hi rendition="#i">I</hi>s
            <seg ana="#technical_invention" type="topic" resp="#np">
                the greatest achievement in the world of music
                <lb />invention
            </seg>,
            as through it you may listen to accurate
            <lb />interpretations upon your own piano of
            over five thou-
            <lb />sand musical compositions,
            <seg ana="#exact_reproduction" resp="#np" type="topic">
                precisely as they were<lb />originally played
            </seg>
            by one hundred and fifty-six of the<lb />world's
            most distinguished pianists.</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_73db1303">
            <lb />Among those who have recorded their<lb />wonderful playing for the Welte<lb />Mignon
            are</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_60560364">
            <lb />No living Pianist has done more to
            <lb />engender a love for music among
            <lb />American
            people than <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/11918625X">Josef Hofmann</persName>,<lb />whose art at the zenith of his
            great<lb />career has been preserved by the<lb />Welte Mignon.</div>
